&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li id="fn:1"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a footnote.
Paragraph two of the definition.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A blockquote with
multiple lines.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;div class="codehilite"&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;a&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;code&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;block&lt;/span&gt;
